            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-477] In ReadOnlyBookieTest, we should wait for the bookie to die before asserting on it</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-477</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now we assert immediately, so the bookie thread has no chance to die. We should only assert after giving it a chance.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
